This paper deals with the complexity of checking consistency of a knowledge base in a specific Description Logic (ALCM), which is a subfield of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The use of tableau algorithms and meta-modelling also suggests a connection to Logic (cs.LO) and Databases (cs.DB). Additionally, the paper involves natural language processing and semantic analysis, which are topics in Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) and Software Engineering (cs.SE).
